Velocita is located in Italy.
The namesake of Velocita Spec, Velocita is the largest track in the game.
Going through multiple iterations, the most recent one was made by Totallynotcap in around 2018-2019.
My version has been completely built from the ground up, and has many changes.
These include an esses section being made from the origional turn 2 chicane, and extra banking on select turns.
